  {"message":
   "SSExactMajority/Convergence/Schedule.lean:15:0: The module doc-string for a file should be the first command after the imports.\nPlease, add a module doc-string before `/-- Concatenate two schedulers at step boundary `k`. -/\ndef concatScheduler (γ₁ : DetScheduler n) (k : ℕ) (γ₂ : DetScheduler n) : DetScheduler n := fun t =>\n  if t < k then γ₁ t else γ₂ (t - k)`.\n\nNote: This linter can be disabled with `set_option linter.style.header false`",
